    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>As written on <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beerware>Beerware</a> there is a famous license
which allows you to</p>

<ul>
<li>give out a beer to the author</li>
<li>drink on the health of the author</li>
<li>send the author a beermat</li>
</ul>


<p>Let's use this approach for club-mate the famous german hacker drink without alcohol but very tasty.</p>

